OL,3,CMiner comes face to face with police
OL,4,Cofficer who arrested him 40 years ago
OL,6,FA miner and the police officer who
OL,7,Farrested him during strikes 40 years
OL,8,Fago this week have been reunited.
OL,10,FThat moment decades ago was captured
OL,11,Fby a young photo journalist
OL,12,Fdocumenting the turmoil of the time.
OL,13,FRichard Williams caught the moment a
OL,14,Fminer was arrested as he tried to stop
OL,15,Fa bus of his colleagues from going to
OL,16,Fwork.
OL,18,FNow the miner, Jeff Jones from
OL,19,FBlaengarw, has come face to face with
OL,20,FMark Chinn, the officer who arrested
OL,21,Fhim during the miners strike.
