OL,6,FWednesday marks 40 years since a
OL,7,Fstrike started in south Wales, and
OL,8,Fother parts of the UK, which lasted
OL,9,Fjust three days short of a year.
OL,11,FFirst Minister Mark Drakeford told ITV
OL,12,FWales the scars from the 1984-1985
OL,13,Fstrike "live on" to this day.
OL,15,FFor Jeff, the wounds of that time
OL,16,Fstill run deep. He said: "Yes there is
OL,17,Fsome resentment there with regards to
OL,18,Fthe police" and those who crossed the
OL,19,Fpicket line.
