OL,6,FHe added: "That resentment will never,
OL,7,Fever, go. As far as I'm concerned -
OL,8,Fand a lot of people would agree with
OL,9,Fme - once you're a scab (who returned
OL,10,Fto work) you're always a scab. You
OL,11,Fdon't cross the picket line."
OL,13,FEven 40 years on, Jeff's view is one
OL,14,Fwhich is shared by a large number of
OL,15,Fpeople heavily involved in the strikes.
OL,17,FRichard Williams, who took the photo
OL,18,Fat the start of his career, has
OL,19,Fcreated a book of photos from the
OL,20,Fstrike, alongside his colleague (and
OL,21,Fnow wife) Amanda Powell.
