OL,6,FTheir book, 'Coal and Community in
OL,7,FWales - Images of the Miners' Strike:
OL,8,Fbefore, during and after,' has been
OL,9,Fpublished ahead of Wednesday's
OL,10,Fsignificant anniversary, and shows
OL,11,FRichard, as well as recounting the
OL,12,Fexperiences of those shown in the
OL,13,Fphotos.
