OL,6,FHis wife Amanda, who wrote the words
OL,7,Fto accompany Richard's work, said:
OL,8,F"Every major anniversary has bought
OL,9,Fcoverage and new information, and I
OL,10,Fthink it has made us all realise just
OL,11,Fhow momentous a period this was. It
OL,12,Fchanged coal-mining communities for
OL,13,Fever, and generally not in a positive
OL,14,Fway."
