OL,6,FTalking about his experience of the
OL,7,Fday he took the photograph of Jeff's
OL,8,Farrest, Richard told ITV Wales: "I was
OL,9,F23 when the miners strike broke out. I
OL,10,Fwas freelancing for the Glamorgan
OL,11,FGazette in Bridgend and we had a call
OL,12,Finto the office one day to say I miner
OL,13,Fhad returned to work at the Garw
OL,14,FFfaldau Colliery.
OL,16,F"I called into the office, picked up
OL,17,Fthe reporter, Amanda Powell, who later
OL,18,Fturned out to be my wife, and we
OL,19,Ftravelled up to the Garw to be met by
OL,20,Fquite a scene really."
