OL,6,FReflecting on how he viewed the
OL,7,Findustrial action in the 1980s
OL,8,Fcompared to now, former policeman Mark
OL,9,Fsaid: "Well looking back on it I
OL,10,Fenjoyed it, the miners strike, from
OL,11,Fthe police point of view in that it
OL,12,Fwas a big operation."
OL,14,FHe added: "Really, looking back on it
OL,15,F40 years later, it was a terrible,
OL,16,Fterrible thing for the mining
OL,17,Fcommunity and maybe that's how I
OL,18,Fshould have looked at it at that time
OL,19,Fbut I didn't actually realise at that
OL,20,Ftime. I was 24. It was just an
OL,21,Fexciting bit of work."
