OL,6,FHowever, Jeff said there was no bad
OL,7,Fblood between the two. Explaining what
OL,8,Fit was like to meet the officer who
OL,9,Farrested him, he said: "It was
OL,10,Fstrange. I don't hold any grudges to
OL,11,Fhim personally because, it's awful to
OL,12,Fsay, but he was doing his job, whether
OL,13,Fhe liked it or not.
OL,15,F"I was doing it because I liked doing
OL,16,Fwhat I was doing. I was fighting for
OL,17,Four existence."
